parameters:
\F[ama_angry]Amma: "You...! Don't get cocky just because you're dealing
with a quiet kid! If you think everything will go your way,
you're sorely mistaken!"

\F[ama_angry]Amma: "A rotten teacher like you will be fired soon! With
someone as crooked as you, there's bound to be plenty of
evidence!!"

\F[ama_angry]\FF[wasio_angry]\AA[2]Washio: "Ugh...! What the hell, all of a sudden...!! It's
none of your business!!"

\F[ama_angry]\FF[wasio_angry]\AA[1]Amma: "You think I can overlook you making this kid cry? No
way, that's why I'm doing this! Get it? I've become strong!
I won't look the other way anymore!"
\F[wata_trouble]\FF[wasio_angry]\AA[1]Wata: "..."

\F[wata_troke]\FF[wasio_angry]\AA[2]Washio: "As if there are students who question what a
teacher does! You should just obey quietly...!"
\F[wata_trouble]\FF[wasio_angry]\AA[2]Washio: "Defiant students are disliked!!"

\F[ama_angry]\FF[wasio_angry]\AA[1]Amma: "Disliked..? Ha...!! The most disliked teacher in the
world is you!"

\F[ama_angry]\FF[wasio_angry]\AA[1]Amma: "Nothing but sarcasm and corporal punishment for the
boys. Touching, leering, and sexually harassing the girls by
teasing them with their breasts and asses. There's no way
you wouldn't be disliked."
\F[ama_angry]\FF[wasio_angry]\AA[2]Washio: "Oh, so you hate me too...?"

\F[ama_angry]\FF[wasio_angry]\AA[1]Amma: "Of course! There's nothing to like about you! You
are...!!"
\F[wata_trouble]\FF[wasio_angry]\AA[1]Wata: "I hate you..."

\F[wata_trouble]\FF[wasio_angry]\AA[2]Washio: "Then there's no problem. You girls can become my
female students!!"
\F[ama_angry]\FF[wasio_angry]\AA[1]Amma: "Huh...?"
\F[ama_trouble]Amma: "Eh...uh..."
\F[wata_trouble]Wata: "...!? "
\FF[wasio_smile]Washio: "Let me ask again. Do you girls hate me...?"

\F[ama_toroke]\FF[wasio_smile]\AA[1]Amma: "No... that's not it at all!! I like you... I really
like you♪"

\F[ama_toroke]\FF[wasio_smile]\AA[1]Amma: "I don't know why... but my feelings for teacher are
overflowing♪ I just can't wait to be messed up by you♪"

\F[ama_toroke]\FF[wasio_smile]\AA[2]Washio: "Is that so, is that so. Heh heh heh...! How about
you?"
\F[wata_troke]\FF[wasio_smile]\AA[1]Wata: "...I love you♪"

\F[wata_troke]\FF[wasio_smile]\AA[2]Washio: "That's right. With this power! I can turn
everything around!!"

\F[wata_troke]\FF[wasio_smile]\AA[2]Washio: "I can see those who despised me groveling before
me! It's my reign!! A school for me!!"
\F[wata_troke]\FF[wasio_smile]\AA[2]Washio: "Gahahaha!!"
Produced by Lunarian
A
